Rats are very smart. They don't bother much with fighting other species. If they lose a couple of members of their family, they pack up the whole crew and move to a new place. They are very near-sighted and rely on their acute sense of smell when they move around looking for food. Therefore, they are naturally afraid when their territory is invaded like this. Those guys wandering around with rocks need to back off and leave the rats alone. The rats like to eat and raise their families, they don't want to fight with a bunch of humans.
